part.text: During a recess in kindergarten we all liked to race each other to see who was fastest every day (yk who always won). There were rankings and everything and it was hilarious 😂. One day as usual we do our regular races and a grown man out of nowhere sees that we're racing, challenges the fastest person to race him, and puts some weed on the line 💀. So I didn't know what weed was but he said $20 worth if I win, and I heard 20 dollars so I went for it. I won, got the weed, but I said "I didn't want grass I wanted money", and he was kind enough to give me $20 dollars 😁. On top of that he raced some other kids for weed and beat them all, but then a teacher FINALLY saw what was happening and the guy ran but he was caught. It turns out he actually helped a kid smoke a little bit of it 💀
